profile:
Reliable HVAC Professionals
 Whether you need a routine furnace maintenance or a furnace repair or an air conditioning repair, Ron Ball Refrigeration is available to handle all of your heating, cooling and ventilation needs. We continually strive to exceed expectations by ensuring that each client receives the very best service. 

Being a Bryant Factory Authorized Dealer, we attend countless hours of technical training to ensure that our technicians are up to date on the equipment that is available on the market today. All of our technicians are licensed.
services:
Furnaces,
Air conditioners,
Heat pumps,
Hot water tanks,
Hot water on demand systems,
Boilers,
Radiant floor heating,
Geothermal systems,
Heat recovery ventilators,
Humidifiers,
Air purification systems,
​Pool heaters
